Scott COOPER, Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
CITY OF REINBECK, Reinbeck Telecommunications Utility, and Tim Johnson, Mayor of the City of Reinbeck, Defendants-Appellees. No. 18-1170 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed May 1, 2019

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

See Iowa R. App. P. 6.904

Scott Cooper appeals the grant of summary judgment dismissing his defamation claim. AFFIRMED.

AFFIRMED.
